Glacier Vault Lock:
  WORM model[write once read many]
  objects cant be deleted once stored in the Glacier Lock.
  policy cannot be deleted itself.
  Cannot be changed at all as well.
  
s3 Object Lock[versioning must be enabled]
  Blocks an object version deletion for a speicified amount of time.
  Object Retention: 
    Retention Period: specifies a fixed period
    Legal Hold: same protection, no expiry date.
    
  Modes:
    Governance Mode: users cant until they have special permissions.
    Compliance Mode: even the root user cant change till its retention period is released.
                     Higher level of restriction.
                     
                     
